## 1 Installing & Using Typescript

----------------------------------------------- npm init -y
Create "package.json"

----------------------------------------------- npm i typesript
needs node.js

----------------------------------------------- npx tsc FILENAME
To compile file (convert into JS) for browser to undertand
[Browser can't read Typescript]

